# Advanced AI Tic-Tac-Toe

An advanced AI-powered Tic-Tac-Toe game built using Python and CustomTkinter for the CodSoft Artificial Intelligence Internship.

## Features

* Modern dark-themed GUI
* Multiple AI difficulty levels
* Unbeatable AI using Minimax Algorithm
* Medium and Easy difficulty modes
* Persistent score tracking using SQLite
* Animated UI interactions
* Dynamic game status updates
* AI first move option
* Winning cell highlights
* Career statistics reset system

## AI Difficulty Modes

### Easy

AI selects random moves.

### Medium

AI mixes random and intelligent gameplay.

### Unbeatable

Uses the Minimax Algorithm to make perfect decisions.

## Technologies Used

* Python
* CustomTkinter
* SQLite3
* Minimax Algorithm

