## How to Run

### 1. Install Requirements

```bash id="dnfrij"
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Run the Game

```bash id="d9y87f"
python tic_tac_toe.py
```

## Gameplay Features

* Choose who plays first
* Select AI difficulty
* Persistent score history
* Automatic game result detection
* Highlighted winning combinations

## AI Logic

The game uses the Minimax Algorithm for the Unbeatable difficulty mode. This algorithm evaluates all possible future game states and always chooses the optimal move.

## Internship

This project was created as part of the CodSoft Artificial Intelligence Internship.

